quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  83,1,Halkaare woodanii …ìeen ustoo…ìe peese
  83,2,…ìeen peesnatoo…ìe yim…ìe …ìe …óa…ì…ìa timminaneede
  83,3,Si…ìe …ìetanii …ìe wolla …ìe peesanii …ìe usta
  83,4,E …ìee kan fellitaa wonnde ko …ìe immintintee…ìe
  83,5,Woodanii mbo √±alngu mawngu
  83,6,√±ande yim…ìe ummanii jom binnde
  83,7,"Alah, pellet deftere faajiree…ìe nani e sijijiin"
  83,8,Ko hon…óum anndin maa ko woni SijjIiin
  83,9,Ko deftere tonngaande
  83,10,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  83,11,…ìeen fennoo…ìe √±alaande njo…ìdi
  83,12,Fennatah mbo si wonah kala palgu…óo keerol bakkadin…óo
  83,13,"Si Aayeeje Amen …óen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinoo…ìe"
  83,14,"Alah, kono muuri …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe ko…ìe pennatnoo ko"
  83,15,Alah …ìeen de ko…ìe ha…óaa…ìe yiide joomi mum en
  83,16,Refti pellet ko…ìe naatoo…ìe yiite
  83,17,"Refti …ìe wi*e:\"Mee…óee lepte mon …óen; ko …óum woni ko pennat…óon kon"
  83,18,"Alah, pellet deftere …óiggu…ìe nani e ka illiyyiina"
  83,19,Ko hon…óum anndin maa ko woni Illiyyiina
  83,20,Ko deftere tonngaande
  83,21,Na seedoo nde …ìur…ìe …ìadaade
  83,22,Pellet …ìeen …óiggu…ìe ho…ìe e neema
  83,23,E leece ho…ìe ndaara
  83,24,Ina anndee e geeece mum en weltaare neema
  83,25,Ho…ìe yarnee dola omndaako
  83,26,Haa…ótirde mum ko lati misku e …óuum de yo foo…óondir foo…óondiroo…ìe
  83,27,Hombo e Tasniim …óuum ko seewnde …ìurnde toowde to aljanna
  83,28,Seewnde nde …ìur…ìe …ìadaade njarata
  83,29,…ìeen faajirin…ìe ngoniina na njala …ìeen goon…óin…ìe
  83,30,Si…ìe mbirtiima …ìe …ìe ngona e …ìii√±andirde
  83,31,Si…ìe nduttiima e koreeji ma…ì…ìe …ìe ndutto ko…ìe weltii…ìe
  83,32,Si…ìe nji*ii…ìe …ìe mbi*a …ìe ko …ìe majju…ìe
  83,33,…ìe nelaaka e dow mum en ngam reende …ìe
  83,34,Hannde de goon…óin…ìe njala heefer…ìe
  83,35,E leece ho…ìe ndaara
  83,36,Mbela heefer…ìe njo…ìaama ko…ìe mba…óatnoo ko